casebody.data:
HANSEN, Respondent, v. SAINT, Appellant. (City Court of New York,

General Term.

June, 1901.) Action by Carl F. Hansen against Ctto R. Saint. Floyd Price, for appellant. Goodale & Hansen (John McG. Goodale, of counsel), for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment and order appealed from affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
